cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.SY, cs.RO 

This paper discusses reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely categories. The paper also involves combinatorial analysis, which falls under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The paper discusses the effectiveness of an optimal policy, which is related to control systems, falling under cs.SY (Systems and Control). Finally, the paper proposes practical mechanisms, which could be related to robotics, falling under cs.RO (Robotics).
